-research-interview-questions" class="blog-card-link w-inline-block"><div class="blog-card-img-wrap blog-card-img-wrap--xl"><img alt="image" loading="lazy" data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd6" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a813dbbdefa2494efcaf65_COVER_How%20to%20Talk%20to%20Users.%205%20Rules%20of%20UX%20Research%20Interview%20Questions.png" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a813dbbdefa2494efcaf65_COVER_How%20to%20Talk%20to%20Users.%205%20Rules%20of%20UX%20Research%20Interview%20Questions-p-500.png 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a813dbbdefa2494efcaf65_COVER_How%20to%20Talk%20to%20Users.%205%20Rules%20of%20UX%20Research%20Interview%20Questions-p-800.png 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a813dbbdefa2494efcaf65_COVER_How%20to%20Talk%20to%20Users.%205%20Rules%20of%20UX%20Research%20Interview%20Questions-p-1080.png 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/64a813dbbdefa2494efcaf65_COVER_How%20to%20Talk%20to%20Users.%205%20Rules%20of%20UX%20Research%20Interview%20Questions.png 1280w" class="blog-card-img"/></div><strong class="blog-card-title">How to Talk to Users. 5 Rules of UX Research Interview Questions</strong><p class="blog-card-text">Are you planning a user interview? Learn top tips and tricks for writing interview questions from professional UX designers.</p></a></div><div role="listitem" class="blog-card w-dyn-item"><div class="blog-heading ml-lg pos-relative hover-disable"><div>article</div></div><a data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd4" href="user-testing-questions" class="blog-card-link w-inline-block"><div class="blog-card-img-wrap blog-card-img-wrap--xl"><img alt="image" loading="lazy" data-w-id="a1483318-f83b-f15b-e5b5-29f52e7cfdd6" src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5f16d69f1760cdba99c3ce6e/6790bec27717edbaf96165ae_transparent-1.png" sizes="100vw" sr